ADDITIONAL NOTICE — MEDICAL & ETHICAL USE

This Software is intended for research and educational purposes only. It is
NOT a medical device, diagnostic tool, or substitute for professional
psychological, psychiatric, or medical care.

The Software addresses topics related to autism spectrum conditions and
involves interaction with minors. Anyone deploying, modifying, or distributing
this Software is expected to:

  1. Maintain or strengthen the medical disclaimer in user-facing surfaces.
  2. Comply with all applicable child-safety, data-protection (including but
     not limited to GDPR, China PIPL, and COPPA), and accessibility laws in
     their jurisdiction.
  3. Not represent the Software as a clinical screening, diagnostic, or
     therapeutic instrument.
  4. Obtain informed consent from a parent or legal guardian before any minor
     interacts with the Software.

By using the Software you acknowledge and accept these terms.
